        <p>You can add other elements (e.g., images) and provide formatting for the content, just as you would in a topic. If you have markers turned on, you can right-click the footnote icon and select <span class="Emphasis">Footnote Properties</span> from the context menu. This allows you to select a format for the footnote number (e.g., uppercase alpha, lowercase Roman), as well as specify other settings in the Footnote Properties dialog.</p>
